**Operating system or device, Godot version, GPU Model and driver (if graphics related):**
Windows 10 - master

**Issue description:**
In the shading language in godot you can assign to a function.
The following shader code will produce no errors:

```
shader_type canvas_item;

void one()
{
}

void two()
{
}

void fragment()
{
	one() = two();
}
```
